## <example: "OAuth callback fails in staging only">

**Symptom**: Auth works in dev, fails in staging with "invalid redirect URI."
**Cause**: Staging uses a wildcard subdomain (`*.staging.example.com`) but Google OAuth only allows exact match for redirect URIs.
**Fix**: Register each subdomain explicitly with Google. Document the list in `infra/oauth-redirects.md`.
**Note**: Wildcard DNS != wildcard OAuth. Other providers have the same limitation.

_Logged: 2025-XX-XX_
